📜 DevOps Shell Scripts Collection
A collection of production-oriented Bash shell scripts designed to automate common Linux system administration, DevOps, SRE, and cloud operational tasks.
These scripts demonstrate real-world automation techniques used by DevOps Engineers to improve system reliability, reduce manual effort, and automate routine operational activities.
---
# 🚀 Technologies Used
- Bash Shell Scripting
- Linux Administration
- AWS CLI
- Docker
- Kubernetes
- Jenkins
- Cron Jobs
- Systemd
- OpenSSL
- Networking Utilities
- Linux Monitoring Commands
---
# 📂 Project Structure
```
sample_scripts/
├── 01_aws_resource_tracker.sh
├── 02_backup_rotation.sh
├── 03_cpu_memory_alert.sh
├── 04_docker_cleanup.sh
├── 05_service_monitor.sh
├── 06_kubernetes_pod_checker.sh
