# 📌 Scripts Included
## 1️⃣ AWS Resource Tracker
Lists AWS resources using AWS CLI.
### Features
- EC2 Instances
- S3 Buckets
- IAM Users
- Lambda Functions
- RDS Databases
- VPCs
- Security Groups
**Skills**
AWS CLI • Bash • Cloud Automation
---
## 2️⃣ Backup Rotation
Automates Linux directory backups.
### Features
- Creates compressed backups
- Timestamped archive
- Automatic backup rotation
- Deletes old backups
- Retention policy
**Skills**
Linux • tar • Backup Automation
---
## 3️⃣ CPU & Memory Alert
Monitors server resource utilization.
### Features
- CPU Monitoring
- Memory Monitoring
- Threshold-based alerts
- Log generation
- Exit status for monitoring tools
**Skills**
Linux Monitoring • Bash • Automation
---
## 4️⃣ Docker Cleanup
Maintains Docker hosts by removing unused resources.
### Features
- Remove stopped containers
- Remove dangling images
- Remove unused images
- Remove volumes
- Remove networks
- Remove build cache
**Skills**
Docker • DevOps • Infrastructure Maintenance
---
## 5️⃣ Service Monitor
Monitors Linux services and performs automatic recovery.
### Features
- Check service status
- Restart stopped services
- Logging
- Health report
**Skills**
Systemd • Linux • Automation
---
## 6️⃣ Kubernetes Pod Checker
Checks Kubernetes cluster health.
### Features
- Detect unhealthy pods
- CrashLoopBackOff detection
- Pending Pods
- ImagePullBackOff
- Cluster validation
- Logging
**Skills**
Kubernetes • kubectl • Monitoring
---
## 7️⃣ Log Monitor
Scans application logs for critical issues.
### Features
- Detect ERROR
- Detect WARNING
- Detect CRITICAL
- Detect EXCEPTION
- Generate reports
**Skills**
Linux Logs • grep • Troubleshooting
---
## 8️⃣ SSL Certificate Checker
Monitors SSL certificate expiry.
### Features
- Check certificate validity
- Calculate remaining days
- Expiry alerts
- Logging
**Skills**
OpenSSL • Networking • Security
---
## 9️⃣ Jenkins Backup
Automates Jenkins backup.
### Features
- Backup Jenkins Home
- Compress backup
- Rotate backups
- Logging
- Scheduled backups
**Skills**
Jenkins • CI/CD • Backup Automation
---
## 🔟 Process Monitor
Monitors critical Linux processes.
### Features
- Process validation
- Automatic recovery
- PID detection
- Logging
**Skills**
Linux • Process Management
---
## 1️⃣1️⃣ User Audit
Performs Linux security auditing.
### Features
- List users
- Sudo users
- UID 0 accounts
- Last login
- Logged-in users
- Security report
**Skills**
Linux Security • User Administration
---
## 1️⃣2️⃣ Disk Cleanup
Maintains server storage.
### Features
- Delete old log files
- Clean temporary files
- Package cache cleanup
- Disk utilization report
**Skills**
Linux Administration • Storage Management
---
## 1️⃣3️⃣ Nginx Health Check
Validates web server health.
### Features
- Service monitoring
- HTTP response validation
- Automatic restart
- Health verification
**Skills**
Nginx • Linux • Monitoring
---
## 1️⃣4️⃣ Cron Job Validator
Audits Cron configuration.
### Features
- Validate Cron Service
- List Cron Jobs
- Detect duplicate jobs
- Generate report
**Skills**
Cron • Linux Administration
---
## 1️⃣5️⃣ System Information Report
Generates a complete Linux system inventory.
### Features
- OS Information
- Kernel Details
- CPU Information
- Memory Usage
- Disk Usage
- Mounted Filesystems
- Network Interfaces
- Running Services
- Open Ports
- Uptime
**Skills**
Linux Administration • Inventory Automation
