- Docker
- Kubernetes (kubectl)
- Jenkins
- OpenSSL
- sudo privileges
---
# ▶️ Usage
Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Tejaswini2808/ShellScripting.git
```
Navigate to the scripts directory
```bash
cd shellscripts/sample_scripts
```
Give execute permission
```bash
chmod +x *.sh
```
Run any script
```bash
./cpu_memory_alert.sh
```
